text: Dilshan Kanchana (born 4 August 1995) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Galle Cricket Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 25 February 2018. He made his List A debut for Galle Cricket Club in the 2017–18 Premier Limited Overs Tournament on 18 March 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Galle Cricket Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
